if miss olivia can
sit with tru.

01:44.171 --> 01:46.205
[tru babbling]

01:47.591 --> 01:49.641
[micah sighs]

01:49.677 --> 01:52.077
-you need to talk--
-I need to get my mind right

01:52.113 --> 01:53.762
before I can say anything.

01:53.781 --> 01:55.864
She deserves to know.
