-You know, vi,
I'm gonna help you.

03:15.145 --> 03:16.678
-Okay.
-I'll head over to the mill.

03:16.697 --> 03:19.514
[ralph] wait. We need
more help at the diner
than the mill right now.

03:19.533 --> 03:21.617
-What's going on?
-Nothing. Look, y'all
stay close.

03:21.652 --> 03:24.036
[ralph] you need
to stick together,
keep eyes on each other.

03:25.122 --> 03:26.488
Please?

03:28.292 --> 03:30.325
