out of my sight.

03:32.362 --> 03:34.830
-All right.
-[nova bordelon] it's been
a rough night for all of us.

03:36.000 --> 03:37.132
[ralph sighs]

03:37.167 --> 03:39.718
come on, let's get those
sandbags filled, fellas.

03:41.222 --> 03:42.971
[cell phone ringing]

03:46.644 --> 03:48.343
-hello?
-[woman]<i> is this</i>
<i> violet bordelon?</i>

03:48.378 --> 03:49.878
Yes, this is violet bordelon.

03:49.897 --> 03:52.147
-[woman]<i> I am so glad--</i>
-you know, I'm so sorry,
but now is not

03:52.182 --> 03:54.483
-a good time for me.
<i> -I am calling from</i>
<i> jones hospice care facility.</i>

03:54.518 --> 03:56.551
-Hospice? Wait, who?
<i> -I have jimmy dale</i>
<i> on the line for you.</i>

03:56.570 --> 03:57.886
[woman]<i> jimmy dale?</i>

03:57.905 --> 03:59.988
-Yes, I know him.
<i> -He says you're next of kin.</i>

04:00.024 --> 04:01.389
No, I am not involved.

04:01.408 --> 04:04.376
-[woman] [indistinct]
-I am absolutely not
his next of kin.

04:04.411 --> 04:06.311
<i> -He has requested</i>
<i> to speak to you.</i>
