please do not transfer me. I--

04:08.182 --> 04:10.182
-[call beeps]
-[exhales]

04:11.401 --> 04:12.718
what do you want, jimmy dale?

04:13.921 --> 04:15.621
-[ralph] come on, y'all.
-[hollywood] you heard him.

04:15.656 --> 04:16.788
[ralph] come on, fellas,
come on, come on.

04:16.824 --> 04:18.523
We gotta get these bags
to the grains, asap.

04:18.559 --> 04:19.658
[hollywood] dump it up,
dump it all.

04:19.693 --> 04:21.226
We gotta keep the water
away from the fields.

04:21.262 --> 04:23.662
-[man 1] give me another one.
-[man 2] over here.

04:23.697 --> 04:25.697
[men talking indistinctly]

04:25.733 --> 04:27.232
[man 3] first one up?

04:29.536 --> 04:31.470
Y'all, come on, come on,
come on, come on!

04:31.505 --> 04:33.021
Why are y'all standing around?

04:33.057 --> 04:34.673
[grunts] come on, y'all.

04:38.679 --> 04:42.247
Y'all get them bags over,
come on. We got no time.

04:46.954 --> 04:49.855
Yo. Yo, yo.
You good? You good?

04:53.727 --> 04:55.494
Yo. Uncle ra.

04:55.529 --> 04:57.796
[ralph grunting]

05:01.952 --> 05:03.402
[micah exhales]

05:04.438 --> 05:06.738
I think I'm still in shock.

05:07.758 --> 05:08.924
I open the door...

05:10.144 --> 05:11.626
...On my way
to pull the windows,

05:11.645 --> 05:13.128
and calvin was
standing right there.

05:13.147 --> 05:15.347
-[nova] unexpected.
-[billie denton]
to say the least!

05:15.399 --> 05:18.299
And after all this time?
That's a lot to take in.

05:18.319 --> 05:20.485
-[nova] yeah.
-How you feeling?

05:21.288 --> 05:22.287
Honestly?

05:23.774 --> 05:24.773
It felt good.

05:25.776 --> 05:27.192
Yeah, I bet.

05:27.244 --> 05:29.611
You're gonna be able
to say everything you ever
wanted to say to him.

05:29.646 --> 05:31.897
That's huge.

05:31.932 --> 05:33.165
[chuckles] it's even
more than that.

05:34.451 --> 05:35.951
To keep a promise to myself.

05:36.937 --> 05:38.870
To be the woman
I always wanted to be.

05:38.906 --> 05:42.074
To not be someone
who gives into the desires
of the moment.

05:42.943 --> 05:44.609
Who honors her relationships.

05:45.596 --> 05:47.879
Who doesn't cheat.

05:47.931 --> 05:51.316
Struggled with that for most
of my adult romantic life.

05:51.352 --> 05:53.652
And last night,
I didn't cross any

05:53.687 --> 05:55.287
of my own boundaries, and...

05:56.523 --> 05:58.807
-...Proud of that.
-[billie] that's good.

05:58.842 --> 06:01.643
So, you gonna tell dominic
about the night?

06:01.678 --> 06:02.811
I am.

06:03.597 --> 06:04.629
There's nothing that happened

06:04.665 --> 06:05.731
that I wouldn't
share with him.

06:05.766 --> 06:09.117
And that makes me
feel nice for a change.

06:09.153 --> 06:10.369
[billie] I'm proud
of you, girl.

06:11.955 --> 06:13.905
[nova] so?

06:13.957 --> 06:16.825
How did everything go
at prosper's with miss sandy?

06:17.611 --> 06:18.610
She fare okay?

06:19.713 --> 06:22.164
[billie] she did. And I, um...

06:23.500 --> 06:26.251
...Kind of fell asleep
on the couch with benny.

06:26.303 --> 06:27.386
What?

06:28.538 --> 06:31.206
-What? Wow, really?
-[laughs]

06:31.225 --> 06:33.341
okay, I mean, I ain't mad
at none of it.

06:33.376 --> 06:35.510
I know, he's... I know.
Nothing happened.

06:36.180 --> 06:37.212
We just talked.

06:37.231 --> 06:39.097
-Benny?
-Mmm-hmm.

06:39.149 --> 06:40.548
-"talked"?
-[chuckles]

06:40.567 --> 06:43.018
-[snorts] yeah, okay,
whatever you say.
-He's a nice guy.

06:44.021 --> 06:45.404
He's really sweet.

06:47.408 --> 06:49.191
You know what
the crazy thing is?

06:50.661 --> 06:54.079
Is the more I spend time
with other men...

06:55.732 --> 06:58.617
...The more I can't stop
thinking about vince.

06:58.669 --> 07:00.385
I don't think
that's crazy at all.

07:01.722 --> 07:04.089
Think that's you,
working through some things.

07:05.259 --> 07:07.042
Seeing where
your heart leads you.

07:08.162 --> 07:10.362
You're on a grand adventure,
billie denton.

07:11.548 --> 07:12.547
Just follow it.

07:13.750 --> 07:14.833
Go where it takes you.

07:19.923 --> 07:21.106
[door creaking]

07:28.949 --> 07:30.031
billie.

07:30.067 --> 07:32.567
-I need to tell you something.
-Is it my dad?

07:33.603 --> 07:34.953
Prosper is fine, baby.

07:36.623 --> 07:40.408
-I wanna talk to you.
Sit with me, will you?
-Yeah, okay.

07:50.287 --> 07:51.920
It's about jimmy dale.

07:52.956 --> 07:54.723
[nova] what about him?

07:54.758 --> 07:57.225
-What'd that bastard do now?
-He's dying.

08:00.647 --> 08:02.681
Called me from hospice.

08:02.733 --> 08:07.402
Some kind of hail mary,
thinking that I was
gonna come visit him.

08:07.437 --> 08:10.622
The nurse says that
he likely won't make it
through the night.

08:12.326 --> 08:14.743
Oh, baby, I'm good.

08:14.778 --> 08:18.763
I've already said
to that wretch what
I needed to say.

08:18.799 --> 08:20.265
I don't know
what he's thinking,

08:20.300 --> 08:23.835
keeping me on the top
of his emergency list.

08:25.005 --> 08:26.288
Doesn't matter.

08:26.323 --> 08:27.956
I said my piece.

08:29.293 --> 08:30.509
I got my closure.

08:32.629 --> 08:33.628
You didn't, billie.

08:35.115 --> 08:38.650
Now, he will never give you
an apology worth a damn.

08:39.803 --> 08:40.969
He'll never make amends.

08:42.189 --> 08:45.023
That's his burden
to carry into...

08:46.443 --> 08:47.943
...Whatever lies
ahead for him.

08:50.781 --> 08:51.980
But in facing him...

08:53.200 --> 08:54.799
...Looking him in the eye

08:54.835 --> 08:57.485
one more time,
declaring your truth...

08:58.455 --> 09:00.205
...Can help you in any way...

09:01.858 --> 09:03.158
...Now is the time to do it.

09:07.831 --> 09:09.164
I want that. I wanna...

09:10.717 --> 09:12.334
I want, I want closure.

09:13.387 --> 09:14.386
Baby.

09:17.724 --> 09:19.791
Just because this helped me...

09:21.645 --> 09:23.361
...Doesn't mean it's gonna
be the same for you.

09:25.232 --> 09:27.515
Everyone has to come
to these things

09:27.550 --> 09:29.568
or not come to these things...

09:31.388 --> 09:34.856
...In they own time,
and in they own way.

09:36.743 --> 09:39.828
I want it, I'm...
Uh, um, I wanna see him.

09:42.082 --> 09:43.415
I wanna see him.

09:48.055 --> 09:49.254
U in here?

09:49.289 --> 09:51.973
Oh, sweetie, what...
Baby, what's going on?

09:52.926 --> 09:55.760
-[sniffles]
-darla, baby, what happened?

09:57.598 --> 10:00.732
It's just a tough moment.
I'm, I'm okay.

10:01.551 --> 10:04.436
No. Baby, you are not okay.

10:05.489 --> 10:07.922
In here, alone, shaking?

10:09.809 --> 10:10.775
That's not okay.

10:12.646 --> 10:14.579
What's going on, darla?
Tell me.

10:14.615 --> 10:16.448
'cause you're
scaring me, baby.

10:17.817 --> 10:21.736
It's... It's, it's about
the man that, um...

10:23.507 --> 10:26.341
[exhales] ...He might
be blue's, um...

10:28.662 --> 10:30.645
...Blue's biological...

10:30.681 --> 10:32.080
[exhales]

10:34.484 --> 10:36.117
he, he's contacted me.

10:38.255 --> 10:39.521
Oh.

10:41.024 --> 10:45.009
I, I, I want to tell
ralph angel, I really do.

10:45.028 --> 10:46.311
And, um...

10:47.314 --> 10:49.314
...I, I know that I need
to tell him, but...

10:50.367 --> 10:52.651
...I'm just so
worried about, uh...

10:54.037 --> 10:55.453
...What he might do.

10:58.458 --> 10:59.824
How he'll feel.

11:00.877 --> 11:03.828
Oh, baby, I am so sorry.

11:06.866 --> 11:08.833
No, no, I...

11:11.288 --> 11:14.005
You faced your fear.

11:16.727 --> 11:18.326
And you got free.

11:22.499 --> 11:24.466
I have to do the same.

11:25.819 --> 11:28.069
You don't have to do anything.

11:29.489 --> 11:31.322
Every situation is different.

11:32.392 --> 11:35.326
Freedom looks different
for each of us.

11:37.714 --> 11:38.747
[whispering] oh, god.

11:40.250 --> 11:41.516
I know, that's...

11:43.253 --> 11:44.719
[exhales]

11:46.156 --> 11:47.522
[in normal voice]
this could break us.

11:49.876 --> 11:50.859
Look.

11:52.262 --> 11:54.879
You take your time coming out.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.266
You're gonna be okay.

12:00.270 --> 12:01.269
[whispering] okay.

12:03.540 --> 12:04.539
It's gonna be okay.

12:06.176 --> 12:07.175
Take your time.

12:17.287 --> 12:18.903
I wanna thank you
all for this.

12:20.907 --> 12:24.025
I wasn't the most supportive
of this co-op at the start.

12:27.230 --> 12:30.365
Took a long time for me
to come around to things.

12:30.400 --> 12:32.567
I was in my head about things,
thinking about myself.

12:34.454 --> 12:37.055
But now I understand.

12:38.442 --> 12:39.441
I see.

12:43.063 --> 12:44.646
We are stronger together.

12:47.067 --> 12:48.149
I'm just sorry...

12:49.319 --> 12:51.269
...That it took all this
to make me see.

12:55.325 --> 13:00.061
[voice shaking]
you were doing all this
for our farms.

13:00.096 --> 13:02.263
And you ain't even got
your own to hold onto, now.

13:07.771 --> 13:09.471
I'm learning from you,
ralph angel.

13:11.591 --> 13:12.957
Like I learned
from your daddy.

13:16.296 --> 13:18.179
It ain't nothing
better in this world...

13:20.016 --> 13:22.016
...Then calling
a bordelon a friend.

13:26.256 --> 13:27.088
Thank you.

13:28.825 --> 13:30.325
-Yeah, I love you too.
-[camera shutter clicking]

13:30.927 --> 13:32.110
good work, everybody.

13:32.145 --> 13:33.595
-Yes, sir.
-Time to go eat.

13:33.630 --> 13:35.396
I know everybody
waiting for us.

13:35.448 --> 13:36.447
I appreciate it.

13:37.300 --> 13:39.267
[crowd members chattering]

13:39.302 --> 13:40.134
it's happening?

13:42.372 --> 13:44.639
Hey, joaquin,
been meaning to ask you,

13:44.674 --> 13:46.241
man, how's your pops doing?

13:46.276 --> 13:48.042
He taught me everything
I know about farming.

13:51.848 --> 13:52.947
[quietly] thanks.

14:02.375 --> 14:03.658
Hey, benny, man.

14:03.693 --> 14:06.311
Look, I wanna thank you
for talking to joaquin.

14:06.346 --> 14:07.729
We've had it
pretty tough going.

14:07.764 --> 14:10.682
