they need our attention,

14:13.887 --> 14:14.886
or by support.

14:14.905 --> 14:16.170
That's real.

14:16.206 --> 14:18.940
I mean, these kids
got way more to process
than we ever did.

14:18.992 --> 14:20.508
[benny] you ain't never lyin'.

14:20.544 --> 14:23.862
I know I'd be a completely
different person if I had
to grow up without a dad.

14:23.897 --> 14:25.196
That's why we gotta
hold 'em close.

14:26.149 --> 14:26.998
That's real.

14:29.536 --> 14:30.368
It was off...

14:38.261 --> 14:39.344
How are you feeling?

14:43.416 --> 14:44.549
Soft...

14:45.769 --> 14:46.768
It's flooding back.

14:50.774 --> 14:53.725
You know, I already dealt
with this in my own way.

14:54.861 --> 14:56.227
I, um, [clearing throat]

14:57.397 --> 14:59.397
I suffered a lot of losses.

14:59.432 --> 15:01.232
Real losses because
of what he did.

15:02.786 --> 15:04.068
And I worked...

15:05.104 --> 15:05.904
...Damn hard...

15:07.207 --> 15:08.623
...To be able to stand up.

15:10.744 --> 15:11.910
And I am standing.

15:13.630 --> 15:15.196
-I'm here.
-Yes.

15:16.132 --> 15:17.031
You are.

15:17.067 --> 15:18.800
Jimmy dale was a horrible man.

15:20.620 --> 15:22.286
And the world is a better
place without him.

15:22.305 --> 15:23.554
Absolutely.

15:24.557 --> 15:27.592
He beat up vi...
He tried to rape me.

15:28.628 --> 15:30.595
And now this... Monster...

15:32.298 --> 15:33.798
...Gets to rest in peace?

15:33.817 --> 15:36.067
Well, I doubt
he'll have peace.

15:36.102 --> 15:38.102
I don't believe that's how
the universe works.

15:38.137 --> 15:41.272
Do you know how many times
in my mind...
